21 Section 5. KRS 160.380 is amended to read as follows:
22 (1) As used in this section:
23 (a) "Administrative finding of child abuse or neglect" means a substantiated
24 finding of child abuse or neglect issued by the Cabinet for Health and Family
25 Services that is:
26 1. Not appealed through an administrative hearing conducted in
27 accordance with KRS Chapter 13B;
